    "154880120": {
      "title": "One More Wage Curve: The Case of Belgium",
      "abstract": "Abstract This paper estimates a wage curve for Belgium. We find an unemployment elasticity of pay close to −0.1 for males, but none for females. This may indicate that the female workforce, unlike the male, faces a more competitive labour market."
